# next()

**Instance Method**

Returns the next element in a sequence.

## Declaration

```swift
mutating func next() async -> ARKitSession.Events.Element?
```

## Return Value

Returns an [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARKitSession/Events-swift.struct/Element], or `nil` if there are no more elements.
